w also in use in the English‐speaking world."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":25,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Joseph Popplewell was born about 1430, in Richmond, Yorkshire, England. He had at least 2 sons with Ann Lawford. He died about 1490, in Richmond, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 62."},"et":{"Abt. 1430–Abt 1490":"umbes 1430–umbes 1490","1435–Female":"1435–Surnud","1455–1516":"1455–1516","1455–1532":"1455–1532","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","1532":"1532","1430":"1430","about 1455":"umbes 1455","Abt. 1430":"umbes 1430","Abt 1490":"umbes 1490","1490":"1490","1516":"1516","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","England":"England","Richmond, Yorkshire, England":"Richmond, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt. 1430–Abt 1490":"noin 1430–noin 1490","1435–Female":"1435–Kuollut","1455–1516":"1455–1516","1455–1532":"1455–1532","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","1532":"1532","1430":"1430","about 1455":"noin 1455","Abt. 1430":"noin 1430","Abt 1490":"noin 1490","1490":"1490","1516":"1516","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","England":"England","Richmond, Yorkshire, England":"Richmond, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt. 1430–Abt 1490":"environ 1430–environ 1490","1435–Female":"1435–Décédée","1455–1516":"1455–1516","1455–1532":"1455–1532","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","1532":"1532","1430":"1430","about 1455":"environ 1455","Abt. 1430":"environ 1430","Abt 14